quran[4]{c,v,t}:
  4,20,"Ma teb$am a pbedlem tameﺣ؟ﺣ؟ut s tayev, u tefkam tuﺣ۶ﺣ۶it i yiwet, ur as tekkset acemma. Ma tekksem, d ayen n dir u d abekkav n ﺣﭨﺣﭨeﺣ۹"
  4,21,"Amek ara tekksem imi temyekcamem, u bbwint s$uﺣﺑwen laﺣ۱qed meqqwﺣﺑen"
  4,22,"Ur ppa$et tilawin i u$en ibabaten nnwen, kkes ed ayen iﺣ۱addan. Ayagi, s tidep, d lﺣ۱aﺣﺑ, d dduni, d yir brid"
  4,23,"Pwadeglent awen tyimmatin nnwen, issit nnwen, tissetmatin nnwen, tiﺣ۱amtiwin nnwen, tixaltitin nnwen, issit n ugmat, issit n tweltmap, tiyimmatin nnwen i kwen issuﺣ؟ﺣ؟ven, tissetmatin nnwen ukud teﺣ؟ﺣ؟vem, tivegwalin nnwen, issit id tessekrem n tlawin nnwen ukud tcerkem usu - ma ur tecrikem ara usu, ulac u$ilif -, tilawin n warraw id turwem. Ur zdukulet snat tsetmatin, kkes ed ayen iﺣ۱addan, - ﺣebbi, s tidep, Izga Ipsemmiﺣ۹, Ipﺣ۹unu"
